# Low-Level Design

## Image Service Details

### Class Diagram
```plantuml
class ImageController {
  +uploadImage()
  +getAnalysis()
}

class ImageService {
  +processImage()
  +extractFeatures()
}

class ImageRepository {
  +save()
  +findById()
}

ImageController --> ImageService
ImageService --> ImageRepository
ImageService --> MLClient


